Qingliu, are you OK? I’ll call the doctor.

567
00:30:11,820 --> 00:30:12,460
I’m OK.

568
00:30:12,980 --> 00:30:14,220
The first priority is to put out the fire.

569
00:30:14,540 --> 00:30:15,900
Evacuate people to safe places.

570
00:30:16,140 --> 00:30:17,380
You sure you are OK?

571
00:30:18,500 --> 00:30:20,060
OK, take care.

572
00:30:20,540 --> 00:30:21,660
All the servants, go put out the fire!

573
00:30:21,700 --> 00:30:22,540
The others, come with me.

574
00:30:22,540 --> 00:30:23,500
OK. Let’s go!

575
00:30:23,820 --> 00:30:24,720
Let’s put it out! Come on!

576
00:30:24,940 --> 00:30:25,420
Hurry!

577
00:30:25,420 --> 00:30:26,900
Father! The fire!

578
00:30:28,380 --> 00:30:30,100
What are you waiting for! Help put it out!

579
00:30:30,100 --> 00:30:31,220
Yes!

580
00:30:32,620 --> 00:30:33,380
Wake up, Aoyi.

581
00:30:36,220 --> 00:30:36,700
Oh, no.

582
00:30:37,300 --> 00:30:38,620
Wu Lin, go get some water.

583
00:30:38,820 --> 00:30:39,220
Yes!

584
00:30:40,260 --> 00:30:40,820
Aoyi!

585
00:31:00,700 --> 00:31:01,180
Aoyi.

586
00:31:02,460 --> 00:31:02,900
Aoyi.

587
00:31:05,900 --> 00:31:06,580
Do you feel better?

588
00:31:30,460 --> 00:31:31,620
It’s OK. I can do this myself.

589
00:31:40,460 --> 00:31:41,540
Your hand is burnt.

590
00:31:42,460 --> 00:31:43,100
It’s OK.

591
00:31:48,020 --> 00:31:48,900
Over these years,

592
00:31:49,180 --> 00:31:50,620
why do you think

593
00:31:50,620 --> 00:31:52,420
the whole Longzhu Gang is following me?

594
00:31:54,540 --> 00:31:55,540
This is nothing.

595
00:31:59,900 --> 00:32:00,940
It’s a miracle for you

596
00:32:01,260 --> 00:32:02,220
to survive so many years.

597
00:32:18,180 --> 00:32:19,140
Are you better?

598
00:32:19,460 --> 00:32:20,420
Yeah.

599
00:33:05,380 --> 00:33:06,260
You are awake.

600
00:33:07,500 --> 00:33:08,380
Come on.

601
00:33:10,260 --> 00:33:10,940
Does your hand still hurt?

602
00:33:13,460 --> 00:33:14,460
You know the pain now.

603
00:33:15,100 --> 00:33:16,340
A girl shouldn’t try to be a hero.

604
00:33:16,620 --> 00:33:17,700
Why do you have to save those bellybands?

605
00:33:18,540 --> 00:33:20,620
We are counting on them to make money.

606
00:33:26,740 --> 00:33:28,620
You wrapped this for me?

607
00:33:29,100 --> 00:33:29,900
What do you think?

608
00:33:31,500 --> 00:33:32,460
It needs to be changed later.

609
00:33:34,180 --> 00:33:34,700
Thank you.

610
00:34:09,700 --> 00:34:10,300
Well,

611
00:34:12,020 --> 00:34:14,100
thank you for saving me last night.

612
00:34:16,580 --> 00:34:17,500
You know what?

613
00:34:17,780 --> 00:34:19,300
You nearly delivered a crushing blow
to the silk manor.

614
00:34:21,740 --> 00:34:23,380
I delivered it?

615
00:34:24,300 --> 00:34:24,900
Xiaoxian.

616
00:34:29,540 --> 00:34:31,900
How much would we have lost
if the whole manor

617
00:34:32,220 --> 00:34:33,100
had been burn down?

618
00:34:33,700 --> 00:34:34,500
In case of no casualties.

619
00:34:35,740 --> 00:34:37,860
According to the items in stock
in the warehouse,

620
00:34:37,980 --> 00:34:38,900
the finished cost

621
00:34:38,980 --> 00:34:41,100
and unfinished cost of them…

622
00:34:41,140 --> 00:34:41,980
Would have been

623
00:34:42,100 --> 00:34:44,700
632,745 taels.

624
00:34:46,100 --> 00:34:47,340
What if it had caused one death?

625
00:34:50,820 --> 00:34:52,780
According to the lump sum
casualty allowance standard,

626
00:34:53,460 --> 00:34:54,340
it would have been 30 times

627
00:34:54,460 --> 00:34:56,500
the taxes our country collected
in the first half year…

628
00:34:56,740 --> 00:34:57,740
Which is

629
00:34:57,740 --> 00:34:59,940
985,990 taels.

630
00:35:04,700 --> 00:35:05,220
That means

631
00:35:05,820 --> 00:35:08,140
you would have caused more loss to me

632
00:35:08,620 --> 00:35:10,300
than the loss of the whole manor.

633
00:35:13,620 --> 00:35:15,140
So, you don’t need to thank me.

634
00:35:15,900 --> 00:35:18,420
Thank yourself for
not being a bolt of cloth.

635
00:35:19,620 --> 00:35:20,780
That’s too much!

636
00:35:24,900 --> 00:35:26,620
Not only are you arrogant,

637
00:35:28,380 --> 00:35:30,420
you are also stingy and cold-blooded!

638
00:35:30,660 --> 00:35:32,420
How could you compare a life with money?

639
00:35:34,700 --> 00:35:36,100
What kind of parents could have

640
00:35:36,100 --> 00:35:37,500
given birth to such a weirdo like you?

641
00:35:38,300 --> 00:35:38,700
You…

642
00:35:39,500 --> 00:35:39,900
Aoyi.

643
00:35:48,700 --> 00:35:49,780
Qingliu, you got hurt.

644
00:35:50,020 --> 00:35:51,620
It’s OK. Nothing serious.

645
00:35:51,980 --> 00:35:53,740
How is that not serious?
I’ll call the doctor.

646
00:35:53,860 --> 00:35:56,100
No need. I’ll wrap it up.

647
00:35:56,940 --> 00:35:58,100
I’ll help you with it.

648
00:36:02,100 --> 00:36:03,420
The fire was so fierce,

649
00:36:05,020 --> 00:36:05,900
did you go in to save…

650
00:36:05,900 --> 00:36:06,580
No,

651
00:36:06,820 --> 00:36:07,780
I hurt myself when I was

652
00:36:08,100 --> 00:36:09,140
putting out the fire.

653
00:36:30,100 --> 00:36:30,820
Master Li.

654
00:36:33,140 --> 00:36:33,700
Say it.

655
00:36:34,500 --> 00:36:36,580
The damage is not too big.
Only three houses are burnt.

656
00:36:36,980 --> 00:36:37,660
But,

657
00:36:38,540 --> 00:36:39,580
there are two origins

658
00:36:39,900 --> 00:36:40,900
for last night’s fire.

659
00:36:41,180 --> 00:36:42,460
One is in Master Long’s yard,

660
00:36:42,580 --> 00:36:43,860
the other is in the warehouse.

661
00:36:46,500 --> 00:36:47,740
We can almost be sure that

662
00:36:48,020 --> 00:36:50,820
the one set the fire
wanted Master Long dead.

663
00:36:53,180 --> 00:36:54,060
= Xinsilu =
- Let me in. - I can’t.

664
00:36:54,060 --> 00:36:54,900
= Xinsilu =

665
00:36:54,900 --> 00:36:55,340
You can’t.

666
00:36:56,420 --> 00:36:57,100
You can’t get in.

667
00:36:57,100 --> 00:36:59,220
- Just let me in, let me in!
- What’s going on?

668
00:36:59,860 --> 00:37:00,620
Manager Yan.

669
00:37:00,860 --> 00:37:01,500
You may leave.

670
00:37:01,660 --> 00:37:01,980
Yes.

671
00:37:04,140 --> 00:37:04,780
You are right on time.

672
00:37:05,060 --> 00:37:06,420
Let me in, I want to see our Chief.

673
00:37:07,700 --> 00:37:09,420
She just got a minor wound on her hand.

674
00:37:09,420 --> 00:37:11,420
She’s hurt? Step aside.

675
00:37:40,060 --> 00:37:40,540
You…

676
00:37:42,020 --> 00:37:43,540
I’m sorry. I…

677
00:37:43,940 --> 00:37:44,940
I don’t believe it!

678
00:37:45,100 --> 00:37:46,100
I’ll get in no matter what!

679
00:37:47,260 --> 00:37:48,100
I dare you touch me again!

680
00:37:48,660 --> 00:37:50,460
- I dare you! I dare you!
- No, please.

681
00:37:51,060 --> 00:37:53,340
I… I won’t touch you.

682
00:37:53,820 --> 00:37:55,660
But they are in there
investigating the case now.

683
00:37:55,940 --> 00:37:57,660
= Xinsilu =
You’d cause some misunderstanding if you get in,

684
00:37:58,580 --> 00:38:00,500
and that would do no good to Master Long.

685
00:38:05,740 --> 00:38:07,420
Believe me, once there’s a chance,

686
00:38:07,740 --> 00:38:08,660
I’ll definitely let you in.

687
00:38:10,580 --> 00:38:11,060
Really?

688
00:38:12,060 --> 00:38:12,940
If I lie to you,

689
00:38:15,700 --> 00:38:19,260
let me… let me end up with no wife.

690
00:38:28,380 --> 00:38:28,820
Deal.

691
00:38:33,140 --> 00:38:33,860
You know what?

692
00:38:34,180 --> 00:38:35,940
I found a book days ago

693
00:38:36,020 --> 00:38:37,980
which is full of the love letters

694
00:38:37,980 --> 00:38:39,780
from those concubines out of favor
to the emperor.

695
00:38:39,780 --> 00:38:40,540
In this critical time,

696
00:38:40,540 --> 00:38:41,620
