697
00:38:41,780 --> 00:38:42,900
I warn you,

698
00:38:42,900 --> 00:38:44,460
if I can’t meet our Chief in a few days,

699
00:38:44,540 --> 00:38:44,820
I’ll…

700
00:38:53,820 --> 00:38:54,740
When you have time,

701
00:38:55,620 --> 00:38:56,980
come for me with your books.

702
00:39:06,940 --> 00:39:08,860
You didn’t leave any evidence, did you?

703
00:39:09,300 --> 00:39:10,100
Don’t worry, Master Qiyan.

704
00:39:10,500 --> 00:39:11,300
Let alone those officials,

705
00:39:11,660 --> 00:39:12,620
